name: Super Fish (SnugGoldfish327)
description:
Super Fish is a Game made for the #TeamSeas Youtubers movement to help the world by cleaning 30M pounds of trash from the sea. you can be a part of this by donating by following the link: https://teamseas.org/

Super Fish is a fun and simple game where you need to dodge the trash by moving up or down with the arrow keys or the W and S keys.

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChL5B7tOtqFm_1gg7Ig7OVg
